      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:35:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙利文称本周达成加沙协议的可能性“非常大”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，以色列和哈马斯“极有可能”在拜登总统一周后离任前达成停火协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</guid>
