    <item>
      <title>为何数以千计的朝鲜人在俄罗斯作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/why-north-korean-soldiers-are-helping-russia-in-its-war-against-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年多来，俄罗斯一直依赖日益亲密的盟友朝鲜提供炮弹和弹道导弹，以在乌克兰进行艰苦的战争。10 月，随着平壤派遣数千名士兵增援俄罗斯武装部队，两国伙伴关系进入新阶段。乌克兰和西方官员称，朝鲜军队出现在战场上是莫斯科的一次重大升级。朝鲜外长承诺，朝鲜将与俄罗斯站在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/why-north-korean-soldiers-are-helping-russia-in-its-war-against-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>他信概述重振泰国股市的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thaksin-outlines-steps-to-revive-flagging-thai-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国执政党事实上的领导人他信·西那瓦呼吁加强监管监督、改善公司治理并为长期股票投资者提供税收优惠，以恢复人们对该国股市的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thaksin-outlines-steps-to-revive-flagging-thai-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非开始营救被困数月的非法淘金者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/operation-to-rescue-illegal-south-african-miners-gets-under-way</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，一项旨在营救被困在南非西北省地下深处的非法采金者的行动正式启动，结束了长达数月的关于他们命运的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/operation-to-rescue-illegal-south-african-miners-gets-under-way</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
